What

Social Network Analysis

Social Network Analysis (SNA) adalah proses menganalisa struktur sosial melalui jaringan (network) dan graph theory. SNA dapat menganalisa bagaimana persebaran informasi dapat disebarluaskan, seberapa cepat, dan siapa aktor paling berpengaruh dalam efektifitas penyebaran informasi tersebut. SNA juga dapat digunakan untuk melihat potensi pasar di sosial media dilihat dari persaingan network antar industri serupa.

Project goals:
- Membuat SNA dari data percakapan Twitter yang diambil (keyword bebas)
- Menggabungkan SNA dengan clustering, gunanya untuk melihat kemiripan market didalam SNA jika data yang diambil data market potential
- Membuat automatisasi dari data twitter, langsung membentuk network
- opsional kalau sanggup: buat dashboard yang isinya: 1. input keyword # di Twitter yang diambil, output: keluar mapping SNA, perhitungan metric SNA, key player, dan clustering di percakapan sesuai keyword. 2. input keyword dari list-of-user yang mau dilihat networknya, output: gambar network, clustering, potential market, dan highest contributive account didalam network (gambar bawah)
- Checklist probation :)

Contoh implementasi SNA dalam melihat persebaran folowers Instagram & clustering dari 22 PTS terbaik di Indonesia

Potential Uses

  • For Algoritma itself:
    • mapping our potential consumer in social media. for example: gather (scrap) all person who follow similar industry like Algoritma (decoding, dqlab, udemy, lambda school, etc). From that person, gather all of their followin then calculate Betwenness centrality, eigen vector, page rank, closeness centrality (metrics you’ll learn in SNA) from their network. thus you’ll get list of person who, which is considered based on SNA metrics calculation, is the best person who can spread information fast, wide, and effective.

How to do it:

note: belum pernah SNA complex di R. jadi ini gambaran besar yang aku tau
- build Twitter data scrapper (streaming and not)
- find out how create nodes and edges dataframe from raw twitter data from rtweet library
- create network and visualize it as fancy as you can
- create clustering from network and implement it on network
- Analyze SNA (all availiable metric)

Comparison on other algorithm/app

Similiar app:

  • Gephi: An open-source software created especially for network analysis
    • pros: easy to use, fancy visualization, lots of plugin, easy metrics calculation
    • cons: RAM killer (seriously tho), community is dead since 2016 (no new plugin), minimum flexibility

So why R?

supported library for doing SNA in R

library(tidyverse) #for data wrangling. very helpfull for preparing nodes and edges data
library(network)
library(igraph)
library(tidygraph)
library(ggraph)
library(visNetwork)
library(networkD3)
# for twitter
library(rtweet)
  • Pros:
    • high flexibility and customization for analysis
    • Dashboard like shinny will very helpfull for public use (documentation)
    • Computer-friendly (it’ll not harm our pc as hurt as other apps :( )
    • Can be combined with other ML/algorithm. for example: creat clustering (kmeans etc) from builded network
  • Cons:
    • Coding (when other apps can easily just drag and drop)
    • standard visualization
    • minimun troubleshoot in the internet
